GetTerminationScheduleOutput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:GetTerminationScheduleResponse xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:GetTerminationScheduleResult>
    <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
    <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
    <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
    <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
    <tns:Future>
     <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
     <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
     <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
     <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
     <tns:Symbol>string</tns:Symbol>
     <tns:Name>string</tns:Name>
     <tns:Month><!-- mandatory -->3</tns:Month>
     <tns:Year><!-- mandatory -->3</tns:Year>
     <tns:Exchange>string</tns:Exchange>
     <tns:ExchangeSymbol>string</tns:ExchangeSymbol>
     <tns:Type><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Type>
    </tns:Future>
    <tns:TerminationDay>string</tns:TerminationDay>
    <tns:NoticeDay>string</tns:NoticeDay>
    <tns:AllocationOfDeliveries>string</tns:AllocationOfDeliveries>
    <tns:FirstDeliveryDay>string</tns:FirstDeliveryDay>
    <tns:LastDeliveryday>string</tns:LastDeliveryday>
    <tns:Status><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Status>
   </tns:GetTerminationScheduleResult>
  </tns:GetTerminationScheduleResponse>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>

ListExchangesOutput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Body>

   <tns:ListExchangesResult>

     <tns:Name>string</tns:Name>
     <tns:Supported><!-- mandatory -->true</tns:Supported>
    </tns:Exchange>
   </tns:ListExchangesResult>
  </tns:ListExchangesResponse>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
